sub_title: Freelance science journalist and communication officer at the institute for Life Science and Technology
summary: Science journalist with a passion for science communication and everything related to chemistry. I write articles about the newest developments in chemistry, communicate about the developments in the Institute for Life Science & Technology at the Hanze University of Applied Science and organize events. My goal is to show people how inspiring and beautiful science and chemistry can be.
